Feature Roadmap:

New Features:

- flagbanning
- easier image uploading (drag/drop into chat, paste file from clipboard, etc)
- custom emojis
- gif searching
- DM user by clicking their avatar
- Premium messages (only viewable by Premium users)
- more fonts (adobe source code pro)
- some kind of gambling polls

Old/boring Features:

- stream size controls
- @everyone for moderators/admins
- click on name in "people here now" to @
- gifting Premium
- lights and fx options
- ping sound when @'d
- confirmation modal on banning and deleting
- easy stream channel adding
- accept donations (https://support.stripe.com/questions/how-to-accept-donations-through-stripe)
- autocomplete @, DM username, mod username, and ban user username
- chat in separate window
- allow blocking DMs
- API for custom styling (badges for streamers, etc...)
- add DM search, mod search, and banned user search
- cropping/scaling profile images
- disable anon posting
- reconnect button
- add infinite scrolling option
